#

Herb-Infused Focaccia Bread

45 min
$5.5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Bread

Tags:

BakingBreadHerbs

Description

Deliciously fluffy focaccia bread infused with fresh herbs, perfect for dipping or as a side.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 4 cups
  • warm water: 1 1/2 cups
  • active dry yeast: 2 1/4 teaspoons
  • salt: 2 teaspoons
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • rosemary: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
